---
description: Core repository policy for this Cursor-native backbone
alwaysApply: true
---

- Keep this repository docs-first and source-backed.
- Prefer root `AGENTS.md` and project rules before adding speculative runtime or packaging layers.
- Treat custom modes and background agents as product capabilities, not checked-in file formats, unless current official docs prove a local config surface.
- If MCP is added later, document the chosen server, auth model, and validation path first.
- Preserve the hard fallback: no CLI-native plugin/package loading claims without direct proof.
